<A>__{tony walks down a street shaking an aerosol can.}
<T>__{music:}
<A>__{johann sebastian bach double concerto for 2 violins bwv 1043, largo ma non tanto he stops at a corner, shakes the can, and starts spraying silly string into the street. as he does this, we hear: a car alarm go off across the street. we see a black range rover. tony raises the can to spray again and sprays. the can emits a squiggly spray and the sound from the car across the street matches the silly string's oscillations. tony puts the can down in astonishment.}
